ore":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:59:17.000Z","msg":"有真普選，香港先有救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n否則只會一直慢慢變壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e41c0b546b88b7b2f57491516fae84c4b91642","tid":1304383,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"開左2個POST叫爭普選完全冇人理直接沉底<br />\n開完PARTY齊齊做中國人"},{"pid":"09a828db7c37e280bde9774e422337034988fae8","tid":1304383,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1379b98d90d538e106013610247f69a9c13dabc3","tid":1304383,"uid":37528,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:04:37.000Z","msg":"2014犯過既錯，而家唔好再犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6f8cb5d15776548deb4980c972ac12e52ee0c5","tid":1304383,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"54e41c0b546b88b7b2f57491516fae84c4b91642","tid":1304383,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"開左2個POST叫爭普選完全冇人理直接沉底<br />\n開完PARTY齊齊做中國人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:02:41.000Z","msg":"之前大家太攰，當係有d news cheer up<br />\n我相信爭普選係人人都想要既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6380722a01aa98905931d7c2c9ef0ffdf5a27bc2","tid":1304383,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"逆權運動七大訴求濃縮版，請大家集中呢七個目標繼續努力，往後示威都要一齊嗌呢七大口號：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.）撤回逃犯修例<br />\n2.）撤回暴動定性<br />\n3.）釋放被捕示威者<br />\n4.）追究警方暴力濫權<br />\n5.）我要雙普選<br />\n6.）拆除所有「智慧燈柱」，永不重建<br />\n7.）永不引入「社會信用制度」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，一日未完全令政府承諾呢七大訴求，一日呢場運動都唔可以完"},{"pid":"07041c9a51368d4fe48f2d2c954